  "description": {
    "canonical": "Forma that can apply the UMBRA polarity.\n\nThis shape-altering component is fundamental to Orokin construction. Allows you to change the polarity of a mod slot on a Warframe or Melee Weapon to UMBRA polarity and then resets their affinity to Unranked. This can only be used on max Rank Warframes and Melee Weapons.",
    "display": "可以设置 UMBRA 极性的 Forma。\n\n这个非固定形态的零件是 Orokin 时代建筑中不可或缺的基础构件。它可以改变战甲或武器的极性槽至 UMBRA 极性，并将其等级重置为无等级。这项物品只能用于满级的战甲及近战武器。"
  },
